title: New: Elite Gymnastics – Life / Trap
content:
Elite Gymnastics may well have just ‘won’ the title Best Beat of 2012 with this hypnotic, trance inducing new track Life / Trap.

Featuring the ever-lethargic vocals and with CFCF on production duties, you can guarantee that you’re on to a winner. Oh, and as always, they’re in an ever optimistic mood; ‘you think your life’s a circle but it’s a decline’. Brilliant. Life / Trap features on RUIN 4 which was released on 8 May available to purchase here.
